that they're furthering.

01:14:58.390 --> 01:15:00.900
And one of the other things
that I'm interested in

01:15:00.900 --> 01:15:04.294
is how a lot of the time
those personas get branded,

01:15:04.294 --> 01:15:05.960
that people start
thinking of themselves

01:15:05.960 --> 01:15:08.420
as using advertising and
marketing strategies in using

01:15:08.420 --> 01:15:10.440
social media and
reaching out to others,

01:15:10.440 --> 01:15:12.270
and I think that that's
the kind of thing

01:15:12.270 --> 01:15:14.909
that the qualitative
work that you're doing,

01:15:14.909 --> 01:15:16.700
that Lyle is talking
about, that can really

01:15:16.700 --> 01:15:18.991
add to our understanding of
those types of social media

01:15:18.991 --> 01:15:20.620
linguistic practices.

